com.google.api.client.googleapis.subscriptions

Interface SubscriptionStore

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AppEngineSubscriptionStore, CachedAppEngineSubscriptionStore, JdoSubscriptionStore, MemorySubscriptionStore

    @Beta
public interface SubscriptionStore
    Beta
    Stores and manages registered subscriptions and their handlers.

    Implementation should be thread-safe.

    Since:
    1.14
    Author:
    Matthias Linder (mlinder)
